Hannah Arterton https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hannah_Arterton 0 Hannah Jane Arterton (born 26 January 1989) is an English actress. She was born in Gravesend, Kent. Arterton attended Gravesend Grammar School for Girls and graduated from the Royal Academy of Dramatic Art in 2011. She is best known for playing Emma Castle in Netflix Original series Safe (2018).
